Pike
====

.. image:: https://travis-ci.org/pyarmory/pike.svg?branch=master
    :target: https://travis-ci.org/pyarmory/pike
    :alt: Travis CI Build

.. image:: http://codecov.io/github/pyarmory/pike/coverage.svg?branch=master
